'''香妲·艾克曼'''（{{lang-fr|Chantal Akerman}}，{{bd|1950年|6月6日|2015年|10月5日|Akerman}}），[[比利時|比利時]]電影導演與藝術家。她的作品對於女性主義電影與前衛電影有極大的影響。<ref>{{cite book |editor1-last=Foster |editor1-first=Gwendolyn Audrey |date=2003 |title=Identity and Memory: The Films of Chantal Akerman |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lULjtguX9HkC&pg=PA204 |publisher=SIU Press |page=204 |isbn=978-0809325139}}</ref>

== 生平 ==
=== 家庭與早年 ===
香妲·艾克曼出生於[[布魯塞爾|布魯塞爾]]，母親為自[[奥斯维辛|奥斯维辛]]集中營生還的波蘭猶太人，但外祖父母皆死於集中營<ref>{{cite web|title = Chantal Akerman obituary|url = http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/oct/08/chantal-akerman|website = the Guardian|accessdate = 2015-10-10|first = Jonathan|last = Romney}}</ref>；她與母親關係緊密，從小就被鼓勵追求自己的理想，而非在年輕時結婚。<ref>{{Cite web| url = http://www.thejc.com/arts/film/chantal-akerman-my-family-and-other-dark-materials| title = Chantal Akerman: My family and other dark materials| website = www.thejc.com| access-date = 2016-02-27}}</ref>她於18歲時進入比利時的一間電影學校[[:fr:Institut_national_supérieur_des_arts_du_spectacle_et_des_techniques_de_diffusion|INSAS]]就讀。<ref name=criterion>{{cite web |last1=Margulies |first1=Ivone |title=A Matter of Time: Jeanne Dielman, 23, quai du Commerce, 1080 Bruxelles |url=http://www.criterion.com/current/posts/1215-a-matter-of-time-jeanne-dielman-23-quai-du-commerce-1080-bruxelles |website=The Criterion Collection |accessdate=18 August 2009 |archive-date=2015-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151125123715/https://www.criterion.com/current/posts/1215-a-matter-of-time-jeanne-dielman-23-quai-du-commerce-1080-bruxelles |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 電影生涯 ===
艾克曼1975年長達201分鐘的長片《[[珍妮德爾曼|珍妮德爾曼]]》被視為最重要的女性主義電影之一，其採用真實時間來呈現一位中產階級的單親母親日常的家務處理和性工作；1989年，她執導的《[[:fr:Histoires_d'Amérique|美國故事]]》獲選為[[柏林國際影展|第39屆柏林影展]]正式競賽片；1991年，《[[:fr:Nuit_et_Jour_(film,_1991)|日日夜夜]]》獲選為[[威尼斯影展|第48屆威尼斯影展]]正式競賽片。她自己本人也擔任[[柏林國際影展|第41屆柏林影展]]評審團成員。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.berlinale.de/en/archiv/jahresarchive/1991/04_jury_1991/04_Jury_1991.html |title=Berlinale: 1991 Juries |work=berlinale.de |accessdate=2011-03-21 |archive-date=2016-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401005238/https://www.berlinale.de/en/archiv/jahresarchive/1991/04_jury_1991/04_Jury_1991.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 死亡 ===
艾克曼於2015年10月5日在巴黎自殺身亡，時年65歲；在此之前她才因憂鬱症住院，返回巴黎住所十天後便自殺。<ref name=nytobit>{{cite news|last1=Donadio|first1=Rachel|last2=Buckley|first2=Clara|title=Chantal Akerman, Pioneering Belgian Filmmaker, Dies at 65|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/07/arts/chantal-akerman-belgian-filmmaker-dies-65.html?_r=0|date=6 October 2015|accessdate=6 October 2015|publisher="The New York Times"}}</ref><ref name=monde>{{cite news|url=http://www.lemonde.fr/cinema/article/2015/10/06/la-cineaste-chantal-akerman-est-morte_4783566_3476.html|author=Isabelle Regnier|title=La cinéaste Chantal Akerman est morte|publisher=''Le Monde''|date=6 October 2015|accessdate=6 October 2015}}</ref><ref name=liberation>{{cite news|url=http://next.liberation.fr/culture-next/2015/10/06/mort-de-la-cineaste-chantal-akerman_1398190|author=Julien Gester|title=Mort de la cinéaste Chantal Akerman|publisher=''Libération''|date=6 October 2015|accessdate=6 October 2015}}</ref><ref name=guardian>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/oct/06/chantal-akerman-pioneering-belgium-film-director-and-theorist-dies-aged-65|author=Catherine Shoard|title=Chantal Akerman, pioneering Belgian film director and theorist, dies aged 65|publisher=''Guardian''|date=6 October 2015|accessdate=6 October 2015}}</ref>

